sequenceDiagram
    participant Sarah as Sarah<br/>(iPhone, Safari)
    participant Nike as Nike.com<br/>(Merchant)
    participant Klarna as Klarna<br/>(BNPL Provider)
    participant WebBank as WebBank<br/>(Loan Originator)
    participant Chase as Chase Bank<br/>(Sarah's debit card issuer)

    Note over Sarah,Chase: Real-world example: Sarah buys $200 sneakers on Nike.com using Klarna Pay in 4

    Sarah->>Nike: Browses Nike.com, adds Air Max 90 ($200) to cart
    Sarah->>Nike: Clicks "Checkout"
    Nike->>Sarah: Checkout page shows: Card, PayPal, Klarna, Affirm

    Sarah->>Nike: Selects "Klarna - 4 interest-free payments of $50"
    Nike->>Klarna: API call: create_session<br/>merchant_id: nike_us_001<br/>order_total: $200.00<br/>items: [{name: "Air Max 90", qty: 1, price: $200}]

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over Klarna: Klarna widget opens in Sarah's browser
        Klarna->>Sarah: "Enter your email and phone number"
        Sarah->>Klarna: sarah@gmail.com, +1-555-0123
        Klarna->>Sarah: "Enter the 6-digit code we texted you"
        Sarah->>Klarna: 482917
    end

    rect rgb(227, 242, 253)
        Note over Klarna,WebBank: Underwriting decision (1.8 seconds)
        Klarna->>Klarna: Soft credit pull (TransUnion)<br/>Score: 720 - good
        Klarna->>Klarna: Internal history check<br/>Sarah used Klarna 3x before, all paid on time
        Klarna->>Klarna: Fraud signals: known device, US IP,<br/>email age > 5 years, phone verified
        Klarna->>Klarna: Affordability: $200 order, no existing<br/>Klarna balances, low risk
        Klarna->>WebBank: Originate loan: $200, 0% APR,<br/>4 biweekly installments, borrower: Sarah
        WebBank-->>Klarna: Loan originated, ID: WB-2026-04-07-98234
        WebBank-->>Klarna: Klarna purchases loan from WebBank<br/>(assignment agreement)
    end

    Klarna-->>Sarah: "Approved! Your payment plan:"
    Note right of Klarna: Payment 1: $50.00 - Today (Apr 7)<br/>Payment 2: $50.00 - Apr 21<br/>Payment 3: $50.00 - May 5<br/>Payment 4: $50.00 - May 19

    Sarah->>Klarna: Confirms plan, selects Chase debit card on file
    Klarna-->>Nike: Order authorized, capture approved

    rect rgb(243, 229, 245)
        Note over Nike,Klarna: Klarna pays Nike
        Klarna->>Nike: Settles $188.00 to Nike<br/>($200 minus 6% MDR = $12 fee)
        Nike->>Sarah: "Order confirmed! Shipping in 2-3 days"
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over Klarna,Chase: First installment charged immediately
        Klarna->>Chase: Charge $50.00 to Sarah's debit card<br/>ending in 4829
        Chase-->>Klarna: Approved
        Klarna->>Sarah: "Payment 1 of 4: $50.00 charged"
    end

    Note over Sarah,Chase: 2 weeks later (Apr 21)
    Klarna->>Chase: Auto-charge $50.00 (payment 2 of 4)
    Chase-->>Klarna: Approved
    Klarna->>Sarah: Push notification: "Payment 2 of 4 complete"

    Note over Sarah,Chase: 4 weeks later (May 5)
    Klarna->>Chase: Auto-charge $50.00 (payment 3 of 4)
    Chase-->>Klarna: Approved

    Note over Sarah,Chase: 6 weeks later (May 19)
    Klarna->>Chase: Auto-charge $50.00 (payment 4 of 4)
    Chase-->>Klarna: Approved
    Klarna->>Sarah: "All done! $200 fully paid. No interest charged."

    Note over Sarah,Chase: Total cost to Sarah: $200.00 (0% interest)<br/>Total cost to Nike: $12.00 (6% MDR)<br/>Klarna revenue: $12.00 MDR - funding cost - credit losses
